{
  "info": {
    "name": "ArunachalamGPT — Feature 1 (Crowd Alert)",
    "_postman_id": "c2a8f5d4-1e6b-4f0a-9c2d-5b8e6f3a2d1c",
    "description": "Crowd reporting, live status with fallback, predictions, devotee profile, planning advice, admin commands, and the WhatsApp webhook driving the 10-step user journey.\n\n## OpenAI GPT-4o behaviour on `POST /webhook/whatsapp`\n\nDispatch order per turn:\n1. **LLM intent classifier** (fires only when `OPENAI_ENABLED=true`) — understands romanized Indic text and code-mix.\n2. **Keyword matcher** — runs when LLM is disabled OR returns `unknown`.\n3. **Translator** — outgoing text rendered in devotee's saved language. English is pass-through.\n\nThe *LLM …* requests in the Webhook folder exercise the romanized-text path. Without OpenAI, they fall through to the keyword path and reply in English.\n\n**End-to-end smoke test:**\n1. *Admin / Upsert config — temple_open_time* (seed defaults — optional)\n2. *Crowd / Submit raw volunteer message* — captures live status\n3. *Crowd / Get current* — should return `freshness: live`\n4. *Webhook / First contact (Hi)* — language menu\n5. *Webhook / Pick language (1=Tamil)* — saved\n6. *Webhook / Register visit date* — saves planned date + flags\n7. *Webhook / Ask for plan* — returns Step 3 recommendation\n8. *Webhook / LLM — romanized Tamil crowd query* — exercises GPT-4o (with `OPENAI_ENABLED=true`)\n9. *Admin / Run command — ADMIN config rs50_sold_out true* — flips sold-out\n10. *Crowd / Get current* — shows rs50_sold_out: true",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Crowd",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Submit raw volunteer message",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"reporter_phone\": \"9444444444\",\n  \"text\": \"F:180 T50:40 T200:15\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/crowd/reports",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["crowd", "reports"]
            },
            "description": "Body is the verbatim WhatsApp text. Server parses `F:N` (free), `T50:N`, `T200:N`. `SOLD` flips the sold-out flag and leaves the wait column NULL."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Submit structured volunteer report",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"reporter_phone\": \"9444444444\",\n  \"free_wait_min\": 60,\n  \"rs50_wait_min\": 10,\n  \"rs200_wait_min\": 5,\n  \"rs50_sold_out\": false,\n  \"rs200_sold_out\": false,\n  \"source\": \"volunteer\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/crowd/reports/structured",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["crowd", "reports", "structured"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get current crowd (fallback applied)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/crowd/current",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["crowd", "current"]
            },
            "description": "Returns `freshness`: `live` (<2h), `stale` (2-6h), `prediction_only` (>6h), or `closed` (outside opening hours)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Predict wait from history",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/crowd/predict?visit_date={{visit_date}}&hour_of_day=8&is_pournami=false&is_festival=false",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["crowd", "predict"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "visit_date", "value": "{{visit_date}}" },
                { "key": "hour_of_day", "value": "8" },
                { "key": "is_pournami", "value": "false" },
                { "key": "is_festival", "value": "false" }
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Post-darshan history record",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"visit_date\": \"{{visit_date}}\",\n  \"hour_of_day\": 9,\n  \"is_pournami\": false,\n  \"is_festival\": false,\n  \"free_wait_min\": 75,\n  \"rs50_wait_min\": 15,\n  \"rs200_wait_min\": 5,\n  \"source\": \"post_visit\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/crowd/history",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["crowd", "history"]
            },
            "description": "Step 10 of the user journey — devotee's observed wait, fed into future predictions."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "List history",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/crowd/history?limit=10&offset=0",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["crowd", "history"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "limit", "value": "10" },
                { "key": "offset", "value": "0" }
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Devotees",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Upsert profile",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{devotee_phone}}\",\n  \"name\": \"Kavitha\",\n  \"language\": \"english\",\n  \"has_elderly\": true,\n  \"has_children\": true,\n  \"planned_visit_date\": \"{{visit_date}}\",\n  \"home_city\": \"Chennai\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/devotees",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["devotees"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get profile",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/devotees/{{devotee_phone}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["devotees", "{{devotee_phone}}"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Patch profile (toggle children)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"has_children\": false\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/devotees/{{devotee_phone}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["devotees", "{{devotee_phone}}"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get planning recommendation",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/devotees/{{devotee_phone}}/plan",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["devotees", "{{devotee_phone}}", "plan"]
            },
            "description": "Step 3 — arrival time + line + packing checklist tuned to the profile's `has_elderly` and `has_children` flags."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Webhook (WhatsApp)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "First contact (Hi)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{devotee_phone}}\",\n  \"text\": \"Hi\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/webhook/whatsapp",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["webhook", "whatsapp"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Pick language (1 = Tamil)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"{{devotee_phone}}\",\n  \"text\": \"1\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/webhook/whatsapp",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["webhook", "whatsapp"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
